Freelancing start krne ke liye apko kya chahiye ?

Freelancing mein jo sab se apki zruri cheez hai woh hai apka pukhta iraada(determination) ,kay mein apna career kahan develop krne jaraha hn

* Intention
* Importance
* Potential

Yeh teeno cheezain grab krne ke baad apko kaafi saari cheezon ki need hai:

* A laptop/computer with a good internet connection
* An in-demand skill
* Communication
* Workspace
* Portfolio

Smart Freelancer apne pese ko invest krega or apni zrurat ke according pesa kharch krega.Baki apne setup or skills pr lagayega.

Or Stupid Freelancer is pese se apni khuwahishat poori krega.

Ek Rule hai jisko follow krna acha rahega sb ke liye:
"Maintain balance in production and capability of production"

Shuru mein agar koi skill nahi hai Toh apna name,qualification,apna skill jo seekhrahay or seekhne jarahay hai uske baaray mein daalein or biodata waghera daalein,baad mein khudhi banta rahega Portfolio.